#: templates/default/api_keys.html:183 templates/modern/api_keys.html:184
msgid ""
"API keys allow external applications to access the Poweradmin API. Each key "
"is linked to your user account and inherits your permissions, so revoking "
"your account also revokes all its keys. Treat keys as secrets - they grant "
"the same access as logging in as you."
